xtras/99d8e67cc61f2af328e925d986b887a5.webp?t=1726817438\" width=600 height=39 /></span><br>No two playthroughs are ever the same! Unique enemy encounters, items, and randomly dropped cards are generated with each run. Discover chance events where you’ll make interesting choices, meet strange creatures, and uncover hidden secrets about the world, ensuring near-endless replayability.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1600910/extras/a543a7e37881f1fe907afa4a7d34d399.poster.avif?t=1726817438\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1600910/extras/a543a7e37881f1fe907afa4a7d34d399.webm?t=1726817438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1600910/extras/a543a7e37881f1fe907afa4a7d34d399.mp4?t=1726817438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
